lab17: manging boot process.
* on a machine with grphical environment installed, reboot.
* from the grub prompt, start test-only target.
* fromm text-only target, boot graphical-target.
* ensure that next boot will go into text-mode.
* set ssh-server to start in every possible target mode.
* ensure that, incase of failure your ssh service will wait 3 seconds.
